---
// AboutCta.astro — CTA section
---

<section class="about-cta">
  <div class="about-cta__inner">
    <p class="about-cta__lead reveal">
      実績をご覧いただくか、お気軽にご相談ください。
    </p>
    <div class="about-cta__links reveal" style="--delay: 0.1s">
      <a href="/works/" class="about-cta__btn about-cta__btn--secondary">
        Works を見る →
      </a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="about-cta__btn about-cta__btn--primary">
        お問い合わせ →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-cta {
    padding: 6rem 0 8rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
  }
  .about-cta__inner {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--content-padding-x);
  }
  .about-cta__lead {
    font-family: var(--font-jp);
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 2vw, 1.6rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }
  .about-cta__links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .about-cta__btn {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 3px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.25s var(--ease);
  }
  .about-cta__btn--primary {
    background: var(--color-ink);
    color: var(--color-surface);
  }
  .about-cta__btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .about-cta__btn--secondary {
    border: 1px solid var(--color-rule);
    color: var(--color-ink);
    background: transparent;
  }
  .about-cta__btn--secondary:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-ink);
  }
</style>
